title: Shuumatsu Nani Shitemasu ka? Iden: Leila Asprey - Novel Updates
author: Kareno Akira   枯野瑛
description: The story is set 500 years before Sukasuka and follows the titular character herself, Leila Asprey, a former princess who is now the latest and strongest in the long line of Legal Braves who wields the holy sword Seniorious.>
